<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-black text-green-500 font-mono overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 10%">101010101010</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 30%; animation-delay: 1s">001100110011</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 50%; animation-delay: 2s">111000111000</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 70%; animation-delay: 0.5s">010101010101</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 90%; animation-delay: 1.5s">100010001000</div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="mb-32 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <span class="text-green-700 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block"
                >Capítulo IV: La Abstracción Final</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-green-400">Adiós a la Materia</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-green-800/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                En 2019, dimos el paso final. Jubilamos al "Gran K". <br />
                Ya no definimos el kilogramo con un objeto físico que puede ensuciarse o perder átomos.
            </p>
            <div
                class="bg-green-900/10 border border-green-900/50 p-6 rounded-lg inline-block text-left"
            >
                <p class="text-sm text-green-600 mb-2 font-bold">La Nueva Definición:</p>
                <code class="text-xs md:text-sm text-green-400 block mb-2">
                    h = 6.62607015 × 10⁻³⁴ J⋅s
                </code>
                <p class="text-xs text-green-800">
                    Ahora el kilogramo se define fijando el valor numérico de la <strong
                        >Constante de Planck</strong
                    >. Hemos atado nuestras medidas a las leyes fundamentales del universo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <h2
                        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter glitch-text"
                        data-text="YO, EL DATO"
                    >
                        YO, EL DATO
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-green-800/90">
                        Pero mientras la ciencia miraba hacia las constantes universales, nosotros
                        giramos el microscopio hacia adentro.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-green-800/70">
                        Hoy llevamos relojes que no solo dan la hora, sino que nos dicen si hemos
                        dormido "bien". Medimos nuestra valía social en "likes". Medimos nuestra
                        productividad en "commits".
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-green-400 font-bold">Si no se puede medir, no existe.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs md:text-sm opacity-90">
                    <div
                        class="border border-green-900/50 p-6 rounded bg-black hover:bg-green-900/10 transition-colors group"
                    >
                        <div class="text-green-700 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-500">PASOS HOY</div>
                        <div
                            class="text-3xl font-bold counter text-white group-hover:text-green-400"
                        >
                            8,432
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full bg-green-900/30 h-1 mt-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="bg-green-500 h-full w-[70%]"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="border border-green-900/50 p-6 rounded bg-black hover:bg-green-900/10 transition-colors group"
                    >
                        <div class="text-green-700 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-500">CALORÍAS</div>
                        <div
                            class="text-3xl font-bold counter text-white group-hover:text-green-400"
                        >
                            2,150
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full bg-green-900/30 h-1 mt-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="bg-green-500 h-full w-[85%]"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="border border-green-900/50 p-6 rounded bg-black hover:bg-green-900/10 transition-colors group"
                    >
                        <div class="text-green-700 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-500">
                            TIEMPO PANTALLA
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="text-3xl font-bold counter text-white group-hover:text-green-400"
                        >
                            6h 12m
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-red-500 mt-2">▲ 12% vs ayer</div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="border border-green-900/50 p-6 rounded bg-black hover:bg-green-900/10 transition-colors group"
                    >
                        <div class="text-green-700 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-500">
                            SUEÑO PROFUNDO
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="text-3xl font-bold counter text-white group-hover:text-green-400"
                        >
                            1h 45m
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-green-500 mt-2">Óptimo</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .data-stream {
        position: absolute;
        top: -100%;
        font-size: 20px;
        writing-mode: vertical-rl;
        text-orientation: upright;
        animation: fall 5s linear infinite;
        white-space: nowrap;
        color: #0f0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
    }

    @keyframes fall {
        to {
            transform: translateY(200vh);
        }
    }

    .glitch-text {
        position: relative;
    }

    .glitch-text::before,
    .glitch-text::after {
        content: attr(data-text);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .glitch-text::before {
        left: 2px;
        text-shadow: -1px 0 red;
        clip: rect(24px, 550px, 90px, 0);
        animation: glitch-anim-2 3s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
    }

    .glitch-text::after {
        left: -2px;
        text-shadow: -1px 0 blue;
        clip: rect(85px, 550px, 140px, 0);
        animation: glitch-anim 2.5s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
    }

    @keyframes glitch-anim {
        0% {
            clip: rect(12px, 9999px, 5px, 0);
        }
        20% {
            clip: rect(109px, 9999px, 86px, 0);
        }
        40% {
            clip: rect(35px, 9999px, 15px, 0);
        }
        60% {
            clip: rect(68px, 9999px, 10px, 0);
        }
        80% {
            clip: rect(12px, 9999px, 95px, 0);
        }
        100% {
            clip: rect(45px, 9999px, 66px, 0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes glitch-anim-2 {
        0% {
            clip: rect(65px, 9999px, 100px, 0);
        }
        20% {
            clip: rect(12px, 9999px, 5px, 0);
        }
        40% {
            clip: rect(89px, 9999px, 45px, 0);
        }
        60% {
            clip: rect(2px, 9999px, 15px, 0);
        }
        80% {
            clip: rect(45px, 9999px, 66px, 0);
        }
        100% {
            clip: rect(12px, 9999px, 85px, 0);
        }
    }
</style>
